        </p>
        <p align="center">
          <img src="https://github.com/shuzijun/leetcode-editor/blob/master/doc/window-3.0.png" alt="window"/>
        </p>
        <p align="center">
          <img src="https://github.com/shuzijun/leetcode-editor/blob/master/doc/menu-3.0.png" alt="menu"/>
        </p>
    ]]></description>

